TWO DOORS-- OPEN THEM.

70
00:07:34,534 --> 00:07:38,067
NOW UNPLUG THE GREEN WIRE.

71
00:07:39,234 --> 00:07:42,267
<i>YES, THAT'S IT.</i>

72
00:08:02,200 --> 00:08:05,734
