HAPPENED TO YOU?

73
00:08:08,434 --> 00:08:13,067
SUICIDE... ATTEMPT.
NOT SUCCESSFUL.

74
00:08:13,067 --> 00:08:15,400
JESUS.

75
00:08:15,400 --> 00:08:16,968
EVERY SINGLE DAY
I'M FIGHTING

76
00:08:16,968 --> 00:08:18,968
A BLOODY BATTLE
FOR MY LIFE.

77
00:08:18,968 --> 00:08:22,100
AT THE SAME TIME, SOME MORON
IN THE PRIME OF HIS YOUTH

78
00:08:22,100 --> 00:08:25,000
