STRAIGHT DOWN THE DRAIN.

79
00:08:27,400 --> 00:08:31,501
- WHAT HAPPENED TO YOU?
- HEART ATTACK NUMBER FIVE.

80
00:08:32,968 --> 00:08:35,801
SO, LUCAS,

81
00:08:35,801 --> 00:08:38,868
I HOPE THE HOSPITAL'S
BEEN TREATING YOU WELL.

82
00:08:41,133 --> 00:08:44,200
<i>I'VE BEEN LOOKING FORWARD</i>
<i>TO SEEING YOU TODAY.</i>

83
00:08:44,200 --> 00:08:46,801
