WE MAY HAVE TO TALK ABOUT

84
00:08:46,801 --> 00:08:49,033
SOME THINGS THAT
YOU MAY FIND UNPLEASANT.

85
00:08:50,701 --> 00:08:54,968
I KNOW IT'S NOT EASY,
BUT I HAVE TO ASK IT.

86
00:08:54,968 --> 00:08:57,067
WHY DID YOU TRY SUICIDE?

87
00:08:59,300 --> 00:09:02,033
WELL, YOU KNOW,
WHEN IT COMES

88
00:09:02,033 --> 00:09:05,267
TO SURVIVAL
OF THE FITTEST,

89
00:09:05,267 --> 00:09:08,200
I JUST HAVE TO THROW IN
THE TOWEL, I GUESS.

90
00:09:08,200 --> 00:09:09,701
<i>BUT YOU'RE NOT</i>
<i>AN ANIMAL, LUCAS.</i>

91
00:09:09,701 --> 00:09:11,868
YOU'RE A HUMAN BEING.

92
00:09:11,868 --> 00:09:14,000
YOU LIVE IN
A HIGHLY-DEVELOPED SOCIETY

93
00:09:14,000 --> 00:09:16,968
THAT HAS ALL KINDS OF
BUFFERS AND SECURITY NETS

94
00:09:16,968 --> 00:09:18,901
THAT ARE DESIGNED
TO BREAK YOUR FALL.

95
00:09:18,901 --> 00:09:22,801
NO.I DON'T FOLLOW THE RULES
OF CIVILIZATION ANYMORE.

96
00:09:22,801 --> 00:09:25,634
I AM OUTSIDE.
I AM AN ANIMAL.

97
00:09:32,400 --> 00:09:35,367
TRY TO THINK OF LIFE
AS A COCONUT:

98
00:09:35,367 --> 00:09:37,701
<i>IT'S HARD</i>
<i>ON THE OUTSIDE,</i>

99
00:09:37,701 --> 00:09:40,834
AND IF YOU DON'T HAVE THE
PROPER TOOLS OR THE KNOW-HOW,

100
00:09:40,834 --> 00:09:44,267
IT CAN SEEM TOTALLY
USELESS AND FUTILE.

101
00:09:44,267 --> 00:09:47,934
BUT IF YOU KNOW HOW TO OPEN IT,
THERE'S SWEET JUICE INSIDE.

102
00:09:47,934 --> 00:09:52,734
<i>BUT THE KEY IS NOT TO KEEP</i>
<i>THE COCONUT TO YOURSELF.</i>

103
00:09:52,734 --> 00:09:55,067
ONCE YOU LEARN
HOW TO OPEN THE COCONUT,

104
00:09:55,067 --> 00:09:58,934
YOU SHARE THE COCONUT WITH
SOMEONE WHO HAS NO COCONUT.

105
00:09:58,934 --> 00:10:01,934
AND THEN YOU UNDERSTAND
WHAT HAPPINESS IS.

106
00:10:04,234 --> 00:10:07,934
- SHARE THE COCONUT?
- YES.

107
00:10:49,567 --> 00:10:54,434
I AM VERY THANKFUL
AND I WANT TO THANK YOU.

108
00:10:54,434 --> 00:10:56,267
THANK YOU, THANK YOU.

109
00:10:56,267 --> 00:11:00,601
YOU HAVE SAVED MY LIFE
AND GIVEN ME

110
00:11:00,601 --> 00:11:03,067
FOOD TO EAT
AND CLOTHES TO WEAR.

111
00:11:03,067 --> 00:11:05,067
I WISH I COULD PAY YOU
BACK IN SOME WAY,

112
00:11:05,067 --> 00:11:06,667
BUT I HAVE
NOTHING TO GIVE...

113
00:11:06,667 --> 00:11:08,601
- THAT'S ALL RIGHT.
- ...EXCEPT FOR MY SPERM.

114
00:11:08,601 --> 00:11:11,767
I WOULD LIKE
TO DONATE MY SPERM.

115
00:11:11,767 --> 00:11:13,501
NO NO.

116
00:11:13,501 --> 00:11:16,767
