BUT IT'S THE LEAST I CAN DO.

117
00:11:16,767 --> 00:11:20,434
IT'S AWFULLY KIND OF YOU,
BUT YOU KNOW WE'RE NOT

118
00:11:20,434 --> 00:11:22,801
