AS AN ORGAN DONOR.

124
00:11:37,300 --> 00:11:40,133
THERE'S ALWAYS
A BIG NEED FOR ORGANS.

125
00:11:40,133 --> 00:11:42,601
MY WHOLE BODY.

126
00:11:42,601 --> 00:11:45,968
I AM READY TO DONATE MY BODY
AND MY SOUL TO SCIENCE.

127
00:11:45,968 --> 00:11:48,667
