A KIDNEY?

128
00:11:48,667 --> 00:11:50,334
YOU JUST TAKE
WHATEVER YOU NEED.

129
00:11:50,334 --> 00:11:52,133
IT'S THE LEAST I CAN DO.
THANK YOU.

130
00:11:52,133 --> 00:11:55,334
- THANK YOU, THANK YOU.
- GOOD LUCK.

131
00:11:55,334 --> 00:11:58,434
THANK YOU.
THANK YOU SO MUCH.

132
00:12:01,834 --> 00:12:05,501
- THANK YOU FOR EVERYTHING.
- YOU'RE WELCOME.

133
00:12:05,501 --> 00:12:08,634
AND HERE'S A LITTLE
FAREWELL GIFT FROM THE STAFF

134
00:12:08,634 --> 00:12:11,634
TO HELP MAKE YOUR
NEW START A GOOD ONE.

135
00:12:14,901 --> 00:12:16,667
OH.

136
00:13:33,534 --> 00:13:35,734
- WHAT IS IT?
- WHERE'S LUCAS?

137
00:13:35,734 --> 00:13:39,501
YOU'RE ONLY SUPPOSED TO USE
THIS BELL IN CASE OF EMERGENCY.

138
00:13:39,501 --> 00:13:41,133
WHERE'S LUCAS?

139
00:13:41,133 --> 00:13:43,234
WELL, I SUPPOSE LUCAS
IS FREE TO GO WHERE HE WANTS

140
00:13:43,234 --> 00:13:45,334
WITHOUT YOUR PERMISSION.

141
00:13:47,133 --> 00:13:51,033
SON OF A MOTHER FUCKIN'
LESBIAN BITCH.

142
00:13:56,467 --> 00:13:58,567
LUC?

143
00:13:58,567 --> 00:14:00,167
- WHAT UP, MAN?
- HEY.

144
00:14:00,167 --> 00:14:02,067
