IN A MONTH OF SUNDAYS.

145
00:14:02,067 --> 00:14:04,400
BOY, YOU LOOK GOOD AS A
GOVERNMENT CHECK. HOW YOU BEEN?

146
00:14:04,400 --> 00:14:07,334
UH, I'VE... I'VE ACTUALLY
BEEN A LITTLE ILL RECENTLY.

147
00:14:07,334 --> 00:14:09,300
- YOU'VE BEEN UNDER THE
WEATHER, HUH? - YEAH.

148
00:14:09,300 --> 00:14:11,267
BUT YOU'RE BACK ON ALL FOURS NOW,
AIN'T YOU, CAT?

149
00:14:11,267 --> 00:14:12,934
YEAH, DOING MUCH BETTER.
THANK YOU, POET.

150
00:14:12,934 --> 00:14:15,033
- I KNOW YOU'RE A STEPPER.
- HOW ARE YOU DOING?

151
00:14:15,033 --> 00:14:17,100
TOUGH TITTY FOR A KITTY,
BUT THE MILK IS GOOD HOT.

152
00:14:17,100 --> 00:14:19,000
- BUT IT'S FAIR OUT HERE, MAN.
- YEAH, I KNOW.

153
00:14:19,000 --> 00:14:20,934
A LITTLE GRIND,
TRYING TO KEEP A FEW DOLLARS

154
00:14:20,934 --> 00:14:22,834
OF THE LUNCH MONEY
IN THE POCKET.

155
00:14:22,834 --> 00:14:25,701
- I KNOW. ME TOO, POET.
- IT JUST AIN'T EASY, BABE.

156
00:14:25,701 --> 00:14:29,501
OH, HEY, I ACTUALLY FELL INTO
A FEW EXTRA DOLLARS RECENTLY.

157
00:14:29,501 --> 00:14:31,968
- HEY, AIN'T THAT A BLESSING?
- MAYBE I COULD LEND YOU A FEW.

158
00:14:31,968 --> 00:14:34,334
HEY, YOU KNOW,
WHATEVER YOU CAN STAND, KID.

159
00:14:34,334 --> 00:14:35,834
- I APPRECIATE THIS, MAN.
- THERE YOU GO.

160
00:14:35,834 --> 00:14:37,100
SO EVERYTHING'S
ALL RIGHT, HUH?

161
00:14:37,100 --> 00:14:38,534
EXCUSE ME,
I WAS WONDERING

162
00:14:38,534 --> 00:14:41,501
BY ANY CHANCE CAN YOU,
LIKE, GIVE A DOLLAR OR TWO?

163
00:14:41,501 --> 00:14:43,367
- YEAH, OF COURSE.
- THANK YOU VERY MUCH.

164
00:14:43,367 --> 00:14:46,033
OF COURSE I CAN.
HERE.

165
00:14:46,033 --> 00:14:48,200
MOST APPRECIATIVE.
THANK YOU VERY MUCH.

166
00:14:48,200 --> 00:14:50,734
OH, MAY I HAVE SOME,
PLEASE?

167
00:14:50,734 --> 00:14:52,167
- YES.
- I'M HIS FRIEND.

168
00:14:52,167 --> 00:14:53,534
- NO NO, I KNOW.
- HE'S MY FRIEND.

169
00:14:53,534 --> 00:14:55,234
- OF COURSE, OF COURSE.
- THANK YOU.

170
00:14:55,234 --> 00:14:57,400
- THERE YOU GO.OKAY.
- HOW ABOUT ME?

171
00:14:57,400 --> 00:14:59,968
- THAT'S FOR YOU.
- THANKS.

172
00:14:59,968 --> 00:15:02,334
AND THAT'S FOR YOU.

173
00:15:02,334 --> 00:15:03,968
ENOUGH FOR EVERYBODY.

174
00:15:43,434 --> 00:15:46,300
