STRICTLY CONFIDENTIAL.

176
00:15:52,267 --> 00:15:54,234
NOW GET OUT.

177
00:16:33,133 --> 00:16:35,634
LUCAS?

178
00:16:35,634 --> 00:16:38,834
<i>LUCAS, YOU LITTLE PUNK.</i>

179
00:16:38,834 --> 00:16:42,000
- <i>YOU'RE COMING WITH ME.</i>
- WHAT?

180
00:16:42,000 --> 00:16:44,367
YOU'RE COMING WITH ME.

181
00:16:45,501 --> 00:16:48,167
I APPRECIATE IT,
JACQUES,

182
00:16:48,167 --> 00:16:50,634
BUT I-- I WOULD JUST LIKE
TO BE LEFT ALONE.

183
00:16:50,634 --> 00:16:54,234
COME WITH ME, LUCAS.
I NEED YOUR HELP.

184
00:16:54,234 --> 00:16:55,634
FROM THE LOOKS OF THINGS,

185
00:16:55,634 --> 00:16:57,834
YOU COULD DO WITH
SOME HELP YOURSELF.

186
00:17:27,801 --> 00:17:29,934
OH SHIT.

187
00:17:32,133 --> 00:17:35,033
<i>OKAY.</i>

188
00:17:35,033 --> 00:17:37,067
BOMBS AWAY.

189
00:17:57,567 --> 00:18:00,067
AH.

190
00:18:09,000 --> 00:18:10,934
<i>HOUSE OF OYSTERS?</i>

191
00:18:28,501 --> 00:18:31,934
WHY IS IT CALLED
HOUSE OF OYSTERS?

192
00:18:31,934 --> 00:18:35,200
WELL, WHEN I BOUGHT
THE PLACE,

193
00:18:35,200 --> 00:18:38,968
BACK IN THE DAYS,
IT WAS AN OLD OYSTER BAR

194
00:18:38,968 --> 00:18:41,400
RUN BY THE LATE
MR. SAVIOLA.

195
00:18:41,400 --> 00:18:45,200
<i>BUT AFTER A CUSTOMER</i>
<i>CONSUMED A LETHAL OYSTER,</i>

196
00:18:45,200 --> 00:18:47,868
<i>MR. SAVIOLA WAS FORCED</i>
<i>TO CLOSE DOWN THE BUSINESS.</i>

197
00:18:47,868 --> 00:18:51,567
BUT I KEPT THE NAME BECAUSE
IT'S THE NAME OF THE BAR,

198
00:18:51,567 --> 00:18:54,434
AND A BAR SHOULD NOT
CHANGE ITS NAME,

199
00:18:54,434 --> 00:18:56,934
NO MATTER WHAT GOES WRONG
IN THE WORLD.

200
00:18:56,934 --> 00:19:01,701
COME HELL OR HIGH WATER,
WHEN THE SMOG DISSOLVES,

201
00:19:01,701 --> 00:19:04,968
YOU GOTTA TRUST THAT YOUR BAR
IS STILL GONNA BE THERE.

202
00:19:11,734 --> 00:19:14,601
<i>WE'RE READY.</i>
<i>SEND IT OVER.</i>

203
00:19:28,133 --> 00:19:30,434
- NICE TO MEET YOU.
- LIKEWISE.

204
00:19:30,434 --> 00:19:32,834
CHIN LEE
IS MY EXCELLENT COOK.

205
00:19:32,834 --> 00:19:35,567
- MONEYED SALE.
- THANK YOU, CHIN LEE.

206
00:19:35,567 --> 00:19:38,601
MY HEART'S NO GOOD.

207
00:19:38,601 --> 00:19:40,434
I COULD PASS AWAY
ANY DAY NOW.

208
00:19:40,434 --> 00:19:44,767
I DON'T HAVE A FAMILY,
NO FRIENDS,

209
00:19:44,767 --> 00:19:48,701
AND I'M NOT EVEN INTERESTED
IN ANYTHING LIKE THAT.

210
00:19:48,701 --> 00:19:51,334
WHAT I AM INTERESTED IN

211
00:19:51,334 --> 00:19:53,968
IS THAT THIS BAR GOES ON
AFTER I'M GONE.

212
00:19:53,968 --> 00:19:56,534
AND THAT'S WHERE YOU COME
INTO THE PICTURE, LUCAS.

213
00:19:56,534 --> 00:19:59,267
WHEN I'M GONE, I WANT YOU--
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

214
00:19:59,267 --> 00:20:02,467
DON'T LIKE IT.

215
00:20:02,467 --> 00:20:04,601
DON'T BE RIDICULOUS.

216
00:20:04,601 --> 00:20:06,434
YOU USED TO EAT
OUT OF GARBAGE CANS.

217
00:20:06,434 --> 00:20:10,133
BUT WHEN PRESENTED WITH THE HEIGHTS
OF GASTRONOMY, YOU REFUSE IT?

218
00:20:10,133 --> 00:20:12,100
SORRY.

